Hello facebook team,

First up I need to thank you for building this SDK and opening up the Ads Manager via the marketing api. The depth and breadth of tools and solutions that can be built on this are limitless.

---

Our team is working on one such tool, but 3 days ago, our tests started to fail. 
The api is not returning any insight. Only an empty object is returned. Following is the console log of a manual attempt. 

```python
>>> ad_account.get_campaigns()
[<Campaign> {
    "id": "6053..."
}, <Campaign> {
